OL,3,CChristmas in Antarctica: Shortest day
OL,4,Ccelebrations underway
OL,6,FAs the UK celebrates its longest day,
OL,7,Fit's mid-winter in Antarctica, where
OL,8,Fyou only get a couple of hours of
OL,9,Ftwilight.
OL,11,FFor the small community of British
OL,12,FAntarctic Survey staff who live there,
OL,13,Fthe occasion is celebrated like
OL,14,FChristmas, with music and the
OL,15,Fexchanging of gifts.
OL,17,FITV News' Science Correspondent Martin
OL,18,FStew reports on how this incredible
OL,19,Fteam spirit formed at the end of the
OL,20,Fearth.
